      Magic Link gesendet
    </h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
      Bitte prüfe dein E-Mail-Postfach.
    </p>
    <button
      id="closeModal"
      class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-[#F5B400] text-white font-semibold"
    >
      OK
    </button>
  </div>
</div>

